Package: americas
Title: Easy Interactive Maps of United States Survey Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ishara", "Wijayaratne", email = "ishara.wijayaratne2512@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A single function, americas(), that turns a data frame
    with longitude and latitude columns into an interactive Shiny dashboard.
    Points are drawn over United States state boundaries on both a dynamic
    Leaflet map and a static ggplot2/Plotly map, coloured by any qualitative
    variable and sized by any quantitative variable, with controls to shrink
    the markers or show locations only.
